metadata.name: imposter syndrome
metadata.description:
Photograph created completely in-camera using an analog blended negative technique, shot on 35 mm film. Colour added in post-production.

BLENDED is a series of 1/1 pieces that explore the artist's journey and relationship with mental health. Each image is constructed using a technique that evokes a blending of two worlds. The addition of colour ties those worlds together and suggests the presence or involvement of the artist / viewer.

1/1  
Artist: Matt Humphrey 
Dimensions: 6000 x 3773 @ 300 dpi

Physical print available to the first collector of each piece upon request.

License: Can be used to display privately, or in non-commercial settings, or in groups with an unlimited number of participants. The license includes unlimited use and display in virtual or physical galleries, documentaries, and essays by the NFT holder. Provides no commercial rights. Provides no editorial rights.
